description.desc: Increases the range of attack using throwing weapons such as throwing stars & knives.\nRequired Skill : #cAt least Level 3 on Nimble Body#

description.desc: Temporarily decreases the weapon def. and attacking abilities of the affected, even stunting the ongoing attacks. Can't use this skill on a monster that's already in "disorder."

description.name: Double Stab

description.desc: Use MP to throw 2 throwing stars and apply damage based on LUK, regardless of the rate of Claw Mastery.
description.name: Lucky Seven
